formvbc@yahoo.com                                                      ', N'2404601719          ', N'www.platformvbc.com ', 600, 56, 1000, 320, 200, 100, 350, 2626, 350, 8, 2800, 0, 174, N'Jennifer Reap                                                                   ', N'PAYMENT
- $350 
- Payable by credit card only
- Payment must be received by the Age Group Coordinator by the late registration date.  If paying by credit card, teams will have 48 hours after receiving their “accepted email” to make their payment.

VENUE DETAILS
- Location:  Interdenominational Church of God
19201 Woodfield Rd, Gaithersburg, MD 20879
- No food table set-ups are allowed in the venue
- ONLY WATER is allowed in the gym - all other food must be kept in the adjoining hallway or outside
- Campsites are located in the adjoining hallway - NO campsites are allowed in the gym
- Chairs are provided, personal chairs are NOT allowed in the gym
- Tri-pods and other photography/videography equipment must be kept off the playing surface

FORMAT
- Start time: 8:00am
- The first matches of the day will begin at 8:00am. All following matches are labeled ASAP and are approximate with matches beginning 10 minutes after the final whistle of the preceding match. 

- Pool play: two sets to 21 (start at 4)
- Playoffs:"  Match Play (Best 2 out 3 sets to 25, 3rd to 15)
- All teams into playoffs - Gold/Silver
- Medals are awarded to 1st and 2nd place in GOLD

WORK TEAMS
- Each team is required to provide a certified referee for one match during the day in addition to the regular work team (scorekeeper, 2 lines persons, second referee). 
- The Chesapeake Region requires an USAV registered and backgrounded adult member to be court side for all Junior work teams.

ROSTER REQUIREMENTS
- Please send a team representative to check-in with the tournament director immediately upon arrival.
- You must have a valid SportsEngine roster to participate in this event.  
- All teams are required to update and verify your official SportsEngine roster at this time noting any absences and presenting a copy of the USA Volleyball team registration.
- Proof of a player''s age should be available upon request.

